uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.network

Class NDirectMatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.network.NMatcher
      • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.network.NDirectMatcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMatcher

    public class NDirectMatcher
extends NMatcher
    Provides an implementation of the reasoning mechanisms defined by IMatcher in which the matching is done directly on the intermediate node/link network-based representations of queries and instances. The matching acts recursively through the networks, taking into account subsumption relationships between the CFrame representations of the node-types, where available.
